{"Id":486,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-mazhonggang","Author":"Ma Zhong Gang","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://alquran.cloud/api","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":97,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"我确已在高贵之夜[注][或前定之夜或盖德尔夜]降示它[《古兰经》]。"},{"SurahNumber":97,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"你怎能知道高贵之夜是什么？"},{"SurahNumber":97,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"高贵之夜比一千个月[即83年零4个月]还优越[此夜崇拜安拉胜于平时1000个月的崇拜]。"},{"SurahNumber":97,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"天使们和精神[吉布里勒天使]奉他的主[安拉]的命令带着对一切事务的判决在那个夜里降示。"},{"SurahNumber":97,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"那个夜是平安的，直到黎明显现。"}]}